text: Catharina Cornelia Adriana Maria "Carry" van Gool-Floris (born 19 September 1953) is a Dutch retired archer. Van Gool-Floris competed at the 1980 Summer Olympics and the 1984 Summer Olympics.Carry van Gool-FlorisCatherina VAN GOOL- FLORIS == References == Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch archers Category:Olympians for the Netherlands Category:Sportspeople from North Brabant
